do Tutorial.tutorial_show_portrait("narrator", "left")
narrator: Different terrain has different movement cost.\
Water tiles cost 3 movement.\
Grass tiles cost 2 movement.\
Road tiles cost 1 movement.
narrator: Try moving to the RED mark across the small river.
